item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Kylie Minogue - KM94, Rapino Brothers Sessions in Lossless
item.description:
These five full, unreleased tracks from studio sessions Kylie Minogue had with The Rapino Brothers (for her 5th, self titled album released in 1994) leaked in lossless years ago “on a forum”. Hopefully someone here downloaded and stored them?

01. Aston Martin
02. Love Is On The Line
03 Living For Your Loving (And I’m Feeling Fine)
04. For All I’m Worth
05. Our Lovin’/ Light I Was Looking For?

Someone has made a fake version that purports to be lossless but is downscaled to 128 kbps in WAV file containers. (Obviously I’m not looking for the fake version).

Im only looking for the genuine Spek checkable, un-retouched lossless files.
item.author: Lexie
